---
title: Smart Southwest-Style Mini Pork Patty Bowls with Black Bean and Charred Corn Salad
description: Mini pork patties seasoned with Southwest spices brim with flavour on top of this beautiful bowl packed with fresh herbs, veggies and beans. A refreshing lime crema is dolloped on top to give it a zesty brightness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-de-mini-galettes-de-porc-a-la-sud-ouest-f7ed617a.jpg
